H&M STORE RE-LAUNCH | BOURNEMOUTH
data.caption: H&M STORE RE-LAUNCH | BOURNEMOUTH
data.description:
We’re re-opening an even better store!

Join us on Saturday 28th February at 9.00am for the relaunch of our store in Commercial Road, Bournemouth.

First customers who purchase on the day before 11am will receive an exclusive 25% off their entire purchase plus goody bags and fun giveaways. For the little ones, we will have a balloon modeller from 9am - 12pm and a fun face painter 12pm - 5pm. Our DJ will be on the decks from 12pm - 7pm too!

Get ready to do some serious shopping…

data.name: VISUAL MERCHANDISER RECRUITMENT EVENT | MANCHESTER
data.caption: VISUAL MERCHANDISER RECRUITMENT EVENT | MANCHESTER
data.description:
Visual merchandisers, we want you!

Want to work for a global fashion brand? Join us on 29th March 2015, 7-9pm for an exclusive recruitment event in central Manchester for a new step in your career.

Send your CV to VMMANCHESTER@HM.COM by the 22nd March. All successful candidates will be notified by email on the details and locations.

BE SURE TO RSVP TO THE EMAIL IF YOU ARE ONE OF THE LUCKY CANDIDATES TO SECURE YOUR PLACE AT THE EVENT!
